## Currently Working on:
### [resource-mmorpg-](https://github.com/CaseyManning/resource-mmorpg-) with [CaseyManning](https://github.com/CaseyManning/)
> ResourceMMORPG (still thinking of a better name), will be a multiplayer, hub-based game.
> In ResourceMMORPG, players will compete for resources and try to beat each other with weapons, armor, potions, etc. made of their resources.

### [JSSheets](https://github.com/tripplyons/JSSheets)
> A spreadsheet application written in JavaScript.

### [Charable](https://github.com/tripplyons/Charable)
> A esoteric programming language inspired by HQ9+, and designed for code golfing purposes.
